  "bio_raw": "Rukhsana Choudhury joined the University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh as a Lecturer in the Department of Electrical and Electronic Engineering in May 2024. Prior to this, she worked as a Young Leader (Management Trainee Officer) at BRAC Bank Limited in 2023 and as a Lecturer (contractual) at Daffodil International University in 2022. She holds a bachelor's degree in Electrical, Electronics & Communication Engineering (EECE) from the Military Institute of Science & Technology (MIST), Dhaka, Bangladesh, and a master's degree in Renewable Energy Technology (RET) from the University of Dhaka. Her research interests encompass Electrical Energy & Power Systems (EEPS), with a particular focus on Photovoltaic Systems, Power Grid Systems, Grid Stability, and Energy Economics.",
